			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Guys, If the Dev Team really looks here for ideas from us. Please lets remember what a Mage is. 
<br />
Damage, Damage, Damage and Summoned Crap. We are 100% offensive with a pet to defend us. Thats it in a nut shell. 
<br />

<br />
Our damage is done from Pet, Fire Bolts, Fire DD's, Magic DD's, Fire Rains, we have 1 Magic Rain, we do Damage Shields the best in game.
<br />

<br />
When we request stuff from Verant for us. Let's remember we dont Root, Snare, Cold, Poison, Lightning. We don't have Runes or damage mitigation thats all done by our pet.
<br />

<br />
Quilin of Lanys</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
